{"tid":2160932,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"當初呢一票投得畀你，就只係想你做呢一屆，留任等於同意非法議會","createTime":"2020-08-17T09:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T17:48:05.000Z","uid":23094,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8c68ed299e9346d696897080f4c79c83796f453a","tid":2160932,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:27:17.000Z","msg":"點解要換屆？<br />\n因為呢屆睇你唔順眼下屆可以踢你走<br />\n呢個係民主制度嘅基本原則<br />\n<br />\n如果屆期完結，喺冇民意基礎下繼續留低<br />\n等於認同呢個非法議會，認同欽點制度<br />\n況且喺呢個本身就失衡嘅議會，你期望自己可以做到啲乜？<br />\n<br />\n親共派一直以嚟靠反對民主派嚟突顯自己嘅存在價值<br />\n如果有一日議會冇哂反對聲音，咁就會有兩個結果<br />\n一係變到一言堂，從此社會變得「穩定和諧」，啲衰嘢有咁盡去咁盡，但係我哋仲有咩可以輸？<br />\n一係親共派要喺中共、選民面前爭取表現而發生內鬨<br />\n<br />\n及早睇清制度內抗爭嘅可能性<br />\n就好似撕破一国兩制嘅假面具一樣<br />\n咁先係破局"},{"pid":"db3f702c85ff51f2a487e107c5851cf1280518bc","tid":2160932,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0265a48ad5aeebf4abb06623a981af8c76f018b4","tid":2160932,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8922497e7496106d723b789fa3217884728025e8","tid":2160932,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"人大常委決定現屆立法會繼續履行職責不少於一年。你有多支持或反對全體立法會議員繼續出任議員？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/poricdch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fporicdch&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRrTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=f27966ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/poricdch</a>"},{"pid":"c5ebdce1ee38c2e6c250d56bfdfee1844cf81427","tid":2160932,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbdf3e514ff664d0994c39f245423a2eb269a7f4","tid":2160932,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:48:32.000Z","msg":"宜家個問題唔係留唔留任<br />\n而係點樣推動制裁個非法議會"},{"pid":"865cf73c1c41b55fd949da49f3e3881f5bc9dbb2","tid":2160932,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e9125a89fbd83e404a94a29a7ae6a9498af258","tid":2160932,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"販民助議收哂工la<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2630ecee8d5e23b6976f14a5af580e3a5289bf13","tid":2160932,"uid":245849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T11:14:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">邊條食屎狗要非法廷任，<br />\n直接支持人大獨裁決定，<br />\n忽視香港人民選舉公義！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">唔好再自稱民主派！</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講最錯係港共<br />\n港共係人所皆知嘅狗屎垃圾殺人犯<br />\n但唔代表佢迫你就要做！<br />\n<br />\n有個強姦犯姦泛民老母<br />\n之後佢叫泛民姦埋一份<br />\n唔係就要切咗泛民碌嘢<br />\n後泛民主流決定姦老母<br />\n<br />\n泛民算咩嘢受害者？<br />\n<br />\n家陣就係要否定港共，泛民係唔係痴咗線<br />\n佢委任你都死去做，即係認同佢推遲選舉<br />\n認同立會可以再用委任，再認同人大授權<br />\n<br />\n以上加埋有咩嘢後果？"},{"pid":"3ff493b8c1b66a17f00cba4366981e1e29d8e358","tid":2160932,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc4d2aef180ac849898d4ccd172300fd9c85deb","tid":2160932,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQ2Azsx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQ2Azsx.jpg&h=4b66bd3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正所謂食過翻尋味<br />\n胡志偉憑咩咁肯定出年一定會有選舉?<br />\n我講嘅就正正反駁咗佢嘅「選票論」<br />\n民意只授權佢做一屆, 今屆完咗就已經冇民意基礎<br />\n唔存在下一年用選票回應呢回事"},{"pid":"9070ab78a9f8e9cdf258257b6c043207a205235c","tid":2160932,"uid":23094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T17:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}